msgid "RAID-1+0 can survive multiple disk failures: up to N in the 2×N array described above, provided that at least one disk keeps working in each of the RAID-1 pairs."
msgstr "RAID-1+0 pot sobreviure a múltiples fallades de disc: fins a N en la matriu 2xN descrita anteriorment, sempre que almenys un disc continuï funcional en cadascun dels parells RAID-1."

